          "message_id": "547d5ed4-899d-4297-a4a2-2601586c4b45",
          "content": "Now I understand. The rotated top-left is computed by rotating the top-left corner around the center. Let me update the code to store and restore the rotated top-left:",
          "tool_uses": [
