          "content": "Right - the size changes during editing (parley computes actual size), but after exiting, `bounds()` might use stale cached size or approximate size. Let me store the size at enter time and use it at exit:",
          "tool_uses": [
            {
              "id": "tooluse_DKYlsSv2TPGK_35IiP8_tw",
              "name": "fs_write",
