        "content": {
          "Prompt": {
            "prompt": "the effect is now that also DURING editing the text moves (which I don want). Before i moved afterwards. So we have to somehow disable that cached size again OR use some lin alg to update the anchor point (preferable)\n\ninstallHook.js:1 using deprecated parameters for the initialization function; pass a single object instead\noverrideMethod @ installHook.js:1\n__wbg_init @ drafftink_app.js:3182\nrun @ (index):118\nawait in run\n(anonymous) @ (index):142\ndrafftink_app.js:1153 Starting DrafftInk (WASM)\ndrafftink_app.js:1153 Creating window...\ndrafftink_app.js:1153 Canvas created: 1183x897 (physical: 2366x1794, dpr: 2)\ndrafftink_app.js:1153 Window created, initializing renderer...\ndrafftink_app.js:1153 Surface size: 1280x800\ndrafftink_app.js:1153 Creating surface asynchronously...\ndrafftink_app.js:1153 Surface created successfully\ndrafftink_app.js:1153 DrafftInk initialized - 2366x1794\ndrafftink_app.js:1153 Keyboard shortcuts: V=Select, H=Pan, R=Rectangle, E=Ellipse, L=Line, A=Arrow, P=Pen\ndrafftink_app.js:1153 Document loaded from IndexedDB: empty\ndrafftink_app.js:1153 Entered text edit mode for new text shape a36908e3-e46a-4337-b479-034672ab9d01\ndrafftink_app.js:1153 exit_text_edit: anchor=Some((587.9557291666666, 580.8128720238095)), size=(45.6, 24.0), content='Enter', pos=(587.9557291666666, 580.8128720238095), rot=0.000\ndrafftink_app.js:1153 Entered text edit mode for shape a36908e3-e46a-4337-b479-034672ab9d01, content: 'Enter'\ndrafftink_app.js:1153 exit_text_edit: anchor=Some((585.0020954087516, 592.1096219640907)), size=(45.6, 24.0), content='Enter', pos=(587.9557291666666, 580.659412202381), rot=-0.463\ndrafftink_app.js:1153 Entered text edit mode for shape a36908e3-e46a-4337-b479-034672ab9d01, content: 'Enter'\ndrafftink_app.js:1153 exit_text_edit: anchor=Some((584.8532858849421, 591.9608124402812)), size=(178.3, 24.0), content='EnterNewjkkkkkkkkkk', pos=(587.8069196428571, 580.5106026785714), rot=-0.463\n"
          }
        },
        "timestamp": "2025-12-31T11:02:59.045472868Z",
