    "Perfect! Let me create a summary of what was implemented:\n\n## Summary\n\nI've successfully implemented **two major features** for Drafft.ink:\n\n### 1. **Ctrl+A Select All** ✅\n- Added `select_all()` method to the Canvas that selects all shapes in the document\n- Implemented Ctrl+A keyboard handler in app.rs\n- Logs the number of selected shapes when triggered\n\n### 2. **Keyboard Shortcuts Documentation System** ✅\n- Created a new `shortcuts.rs` module with:\n  - `Shortcut` struct to define keyboard shortcuts (key, modifiers, description)\n  - `ShortcutRegistry` with centralized list of all shortcuts\n  - Formatted display method (e.g., \"Ctrl+S\", \"Ctrl+Shift+G\")\n- Added \"Keyboard Shortcuts\" menu item in the hamburger menu\n- Created a modal dialog that displays all shortcuts in a clean, scrollable list\n- Added `ShowShortcuts` action to the UI system\n\n### 3. **Freehand Drawing Resizing** ✅\n- Implemented corner handle resizing for freehand drawings (draw tool)\n- Added `apply_corner_resize_freehand()` function that:\n  - Calculates scale factors based on bounding box changes\n  - Proportionally scales all points in the drawing\n  - Maintains relative positions of strokes\n  - Handles corner flipping when dragging past opposite corners\n\n### 4. **Image Resizing** ✅\n- Implemented corner handle resizing for embedded images\n- Added `apply_corner_resize_image()` function that:\n  - Updates position, width, and height based on corner drag\n  - Ensures minimum size constraints\n  - Handles corner flipping\n\n**Files Modified:**\n- `crates/drafftink-core/src/canvas.rs` - Added select_all()\n- `crates/drafftink-core/src/selection.rs` - Added resize functions for Freehand and Image\n- `crates/drafftink-app/src/app.rs` - Added Ctrl+A handler and ShowShortcuts action handler\n- `crates/drafftink-app/src/shortcuts.rs` - New module (created)\n- `crates/drafftink-app/src/lib.rs` - Exported shortcuts module\n- `crates/drafftink-app/src/ui.rs` - Added shortcuts m