    "Done. Updated both icons:\n- `undo.svg` - circular arrow going counter-clockwise with arrow pointing left\n- `redo.svg` - mirrored version, circular arrow going clockwise with arrow pointing right\n\nBoth use `currentColor` for stroke so they'll inherit the icon color, and are scaled to 24x24 viewBox.\n[Tool uses: none]",
