    "I see! The text moves during editing because updating the cached size changes the bounds, which changes the center, which changes the rotation transform.\n\nThe solution: update `text.position` during editing to keep the anchor fixed. We need to adjust position whenever size changes to compensate.\n\nLet me update `render_text_editing` to adjust position when size changes:\n[Tool uses: fs_read]",
