    "Based on my scan of the codebase, here are **20 features that do NOT exist yet**:\n\n1. **SVG Export** - No SVG export capability (only PNG export exists)\n2. **PDF Export** - No PDF export capability\n3. **Eraser Tool** - No eraser tool to remove parts of freehand strokes\n4. **Highlighter Tool** - No semi-transparent highlighter pen\n5. **Polygon/Star Shapes** - No polygon or star shape tools (only rectangle, ellipse, line, arrow)\n6. **Diamond Shape** - Mentioned as TODO in code, currently just rotated rectangle\n7. **Sticky Notes** - No sticky note/comment shapes\n8. **Shape Locking** - No ability to lock shapes from editing\n9. **Shape Visibility Toggle** - No ability to hide/show individual shapes\n10. **Minimap/Overview** - No minimap for navigating large canvases\n11. **Rulers/Measurement Tool** - No rulers or dimension measurement\n12. **Dark Mode Toggle** - Theme exists but no user-switchable dark/light mode\n13. **Shape Connectors** - No auto-connecting lines between shapes (arrows don't snap to shape edges)\n14. **Templates/Presets Library** - No shape templates or preset libraries\n15. **LaTeX/Math Equations** - No math equation rendering\n16. **Flip/Mirror Shapes** - No horizontal/vertical flip for shapes\n17. **Shape Opacity Control** - No per-shape opacity/transparency setting\n18. **Gradient Fills** - Only solid and pattern fills, no gradients\n19. **Customizable Keyboard Shortcuts** - Shortcuts exist but aren't user-configurable\n20. **Laser Pointer/Presentation Mode** - No presentation mode with laser pointer for collaboration\n[Tool uses: none]",
    "> /save /local/home/patwie/git/github.com/patwie/drafft-ink/context.q"
